 > A community bounty board for Claude Code builders.
 
+## Bounty #3: Destructive Bash Command Blocker
+
+This repository includes a Claude Code `PreToolUse` hook that blocks destructive
+Bash commands before they run. It denies `rm -rf`, `DROP TABLE`, `TRUNCATE`,
+`git push --force`, and `DELETE FROM` statements that do not include a `WHERE`
+clause. Every blocked attempt is appended to `~/.claude/hooks/blocked.log` with
+the timestamp, attempted command, project path, and block reason.
+
+Install in two commands:
+
+```bash
+git clone https://github.com/claude-builders-bounty/claude-builders-bounty.git && cd claude-builders-bounty
+./install.sh
+```
+
+The installer copies the hook to `~/.claude/hooks/block-destructive-bash.py`,
+makes it executable, and registers it under the `PreToolUse` hook for Bash in
+`~/.claude/settings.json`.
+
+Run tests:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m unittest discover -s tests
+```
+
 Building with Claude Code? Have tasks to delegate?
 Want to get paid for contributing to AI projects?
 You're in the right place.
